                "institute": "3INDNSD"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 15UD-Pelletron accelerator.",
                "Irradiations have been carried out in the General",
                "Purpose Scattering Chamber (GPSC) along with an In-",
                "vacuum Transfer Facility (ITF)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The thickness of the sample has been estimated",
                "by the alpha-transmission method which is based on",
                "the measurement of the energy loss by the alpha",
                "particles of energy 5.486 MeV from the Am-241 source",
                "while passing through the sample material. The",
                "samples have been pasted on rectangular aluminum",
                "holders (1.2 x 1.2 cm2) having concentric hole of 1",
                "cm diameter, Al holders have been used for rapid heat",
                "dissipation during the irradiations."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Volume of detector was 100 c.c coupled with the",
                "CAMAC-based FREEDOM software"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Experimentally measured cumulative",
                " (CF+ICF) production cross-sections, deduced (using",
                "RRDs) cross-section for ICF and CF components and the",
                "theoretically calculated (PACE) cross-sections for",
                "the residues produced in the 16O + 159Tb or",
                "                                  16O + 169Tm system."
              ]
            }
          ],
